ikaaro 0.62.4 (2010/11/25)
==========================

This is a Content Management System built on Python & itools, among
other features ikaaro provides:

 - content and document management (index&search, metadata, etc.)
 - multilingual user interfaces and content
 - high level modules: wiki, forum, tracker, etc.

Changes
-------

The documentation, written using Sphinx [1], is now included in the
ikaaro source, within the 'docs/' folder (previously it was in a
separate package). The URL has also changed, now it is:

  http://www.hforge.org/ikaaro/docs

There have been many small enhancements and bug fixes, including:

  #638 Fix non-breaking-space in translations
 #1037 Refactor & improve sorting in the browse-content view, add API
 #1041 Add the non-breaking-space plugin to TinyMCE
 #1057 Tracker: fix sort by title

[1] http://sphinx.pocoo.org/


